title: Macron thanks Australia PM's "delicious" wife
text:
Macron thanks Australia PM's "delicious" wife 5:21pm BST - 00:34
French President Emmanuel Macron thanks Australian Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull and his ''delicious wife'' for their warm welcome and hospitality during his visit to Sydney. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
